HOW IT WORKS 
1. Select your pick-up and drop-off locations on the map
2. View estimated trip fare, ETA, driver and vehicle info 
3. Book your ride now or schedule in advance
4. Pay through the app (Apple Pay, Google Pay, credit/debit cards) or use in-vehicle terminals
5. Receive an emailed receipt at the end of each trip for simple bookkeeping
